      "content": "hey, im sorry to bother u but im kinda freaking out. i feel like my neighbors are doing something to me. like, whenever i'm in my living room there's this weird low hum or vibration and it just makes me feel super angry and anxious for no reason. i dont think im crazy, i can actually feel it in my chest. u think there could be some kind of device or something causing this?",
