      "content": "it literally feels like they're doing it on purpose to mess with my head. i saw one of them looking at me weirdly when i was taking the trash out today, almost like they were checking to see if i was reacting to it. i'm just so paranoid now. if someone actually had a device that could do this, how would they even hide it? like, what kind of setup would you need to make it look like it's just part of the building or something?",
